<subpara id="RM00000276B000X_07" type-id="51" category="05" proc-id="RM0250U___00008Q300000">
<name>INSPECTION PROCEDURE</name>
<content5 releasenbr="1">
<atten4>
<ptxt>Read freeze frame data using the intelligent tester. The ECM records vehicle and driving condition information as freeze frame data the moment a DTC is stored. When troubleshooting, freeze frame data can help determine if the vehicle was moving or stationary, if the engine was warmed up or not, if the air-fuel ratio was lean or rich, and other data from the time the malfunction occurred.</ptxt>
</atten4>
</content5>
</subpara>
<subpara id="RM00000276B000X_08" type-id="01" category="01">
<name>PROCEDURE</name>
<testgrp id="RM00000276B000X_08_0001" proc-id="RM0250U___00008Q400000">
<testtitle>INSPECT INTAKE MANIFOLD RUNNER VALVE ASSEMBLY (IMRV MOTOR RESISTANCE)</testtitle>
<content6 releasenbr="1">
<test1>
<ptxt>Disconnect the C33 IMRV connector.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="A066037E01" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Measure the motor resistance between the terminals.</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>Standard resistance</title>
<table>
<tgroup cols="3" align="center">
<colspec colname="COL1" colwidth="1.38in"/>
<colspec colname="COL2" colwidth="1.38in"/>
<colspec colname="COL3" colwidth="1.37in"/>
<thead>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Tester Connection</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Condition</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Specified Condition</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>C33-5 (IAC+) - C33-4 (IAC-)</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>20°C (68°F)</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>1 to 19 Ω</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</spec>
</test1>
</content6>
<res>
<down ref="RM00000276B000X_08_0002" fin="false">OK</down>
<right ref="RM00000276B000X_08_0005" fin="true">NG</right>
</res>
</testgrp>
<testgrp id="RM00000276B000X_08_0002" proc-id="RM0250U___00008Q700000">
<testtitle>CHECK HARNESS AND CONNECTOR (IMRV MOTOR - ECM)</testtitle>
<content6 releasenbr="1">
<test1>
<ptxt>Disconnect the A24 ECM connector.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="A132309E01" width="2.775699831in" height="3.779676365in"/>
</figure>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Disconnect the C33 IMRV motor connector.</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Measure the resistance between the terminals of the wire harness side connectors.</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>Standard resistance (Check for open)</title>
<table>
<tgroup cols="2" align="center">
<colspec colname="COL1" colwidth="2.89in"/>
<colspec colname="COL2" colwidth="1.24in"/>
<thead>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Tester Connection</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Specified Condition</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>A24-33 (IAC+) - C33-5 (IAC+)</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Below 1 Ω</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>A24-52 (IAC-) - C33-4 (IAC-)</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Below 1 Ω</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</spec>
<spec>
<title>Standard resistance (Check for short)</title>
<table>
<tgroup cols="2" align="center">
<colspec colname="COL1" colwidth="2.89in"/>
<colspec colname="COL2" colwidth="1.24in"/>
<thead>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Tester Connection</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Specified Condition</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>A24-33 (IAC+) or C33-5 (IAC+) - Body ground</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>10 kΩ or more</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>A24-52 (IAC-) or C33-4 (IAC-) - Body ground</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>10 kΩ or more</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</spec>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Reconnect the connectors.</ptxt>
</test1>
</content6>
<res>
<down ref="RM00000276B000X_08_0003" fin="false">OK</down>
<right ref="RM00000276B000X_08_0006" fin="true">NG</right>
</res>
</testgrp>
<testgrp id="RM00000276B000X_08_0003" proc-id="RM0250U___00008Q800000">
<testtitle>CHECK WHETHER DTC OUTPUT RECURS</testtitle>
<content6 releasenbr="1">
<test1>
<ptxt>Clear the DTC (See page <xref label="Seep01" href="RM000000PDK01MX"/>).</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Start the engine.</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Run the engine at more than 3,000 rpm.</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Turn the ignition switch off.</ptxt>
<atten4>
<ptxt>As running the engine to 3,000 rpm, the IMRV usually becomes fully opened. If the ignition switch is turned off under this condition, the IMRV is fully closed and then becomes half-opening angle.</ptxt>
</atten4>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Read the DTC.</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>Result</title>
<table pgwide="1">
<tgroup cols="2" align="center">
<colspec colname="COL1" colwidth="3.54in"/>
<colspec colname="COL2" colwidth="3.54in"/>
<thead>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Display (DTC output)</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Proceed to</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>P2009 and/or P2010 are output again</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>A</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>No DTC output</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>B</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</spec>
</test1>
</content6>
<res>
<down ref="RM00000276B000X_08_0004" fin="true">A</down>
<right ref="RM00000276B000X_08_0007" fin="true">B</right>
</res>
</testgrp>
<testgrp id="RM00000276B000X_08_0004">
<testtitle>REPLACE ECM</testtitle>
</testgrp>
<testgrp id="RM00000276B000X_08_0005">
<testtitle>REPLACE INTAKE MANIFOLD RUNNER VALVE ASSEMBLY</testtitle>
</testgrp>
<testgrp id="RM00000276B000X_08_0006">
<testtitle>REPAIR OR REPLACE HARNESS OR CONNECTOR</testtitle>
</testgrp>
<testgrp id="RM00000276B000X_08_0007">
<testtitle>CHECK FOR INTERMITTENT PROBLEMS</testtitle>
</testgrp>
</subpara>
</para>
